    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>diced carrot</strong> and <strong>grated mushrooms </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables are beginning to soften, add your<strong> mince</strong> to the pan and increase the heat to high</p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>wholewheat tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>wholewheat tortiglioni </strong>for 10-12 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>wholewheat tortiglioni</strong> and return to the pot until serving</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix</strong> and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>dried oregano </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>beef stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min further or until thickened and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>mushroom bolognese</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>lighter cheese</strong></p><p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>drained wholewheat tortiglioni </strong>to the pan and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce \u2013 this is your<strong> mushroom bolognese with wholewheat tortiglioni</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lean-beef-and-mushroom-bolognese-with-wholewheat-tortiglioni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> mushroom bolognese with wholewheat tortiglioni </strong>and top with the <strong>grated lighter cheese</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
